column1: Balduzzi et al. - 2019 - How to perform a meta-analysis with R a practical tutorial.pdf
column2: How to perform a meta-analysis with R: a practical tutorial
column6: The paper is a tutorial on performing meta-analyses using R, focusing on a working example with haloperidol for schizophrenia symptoms, not on interventions for Multiple Sclerosis (MS). It does not address the specified interventions (Natalizumab, SID, EID) or MS outcomes.
